\begin_layout Itemize
The quadratic form
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(\boldsymbol{x}-\boldsymbol{\mu})^{\top}\boldsymbol{\Sigma}^{-1}(\boldsymbol{x}-\boldsymbol{\mu})
\]

\end_inset

is the vector version of a squared standardized variable
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\frac{X-\mu}{\sigma}\right)^{2}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

